26 identified business entity and the motor vehicle, power sports vehicle, or trailer is displayed on premises owned
27 or leased by the other business entity and where the other entity regularly conducts its business. A display
28 under this subsection (4)(c)(ii) may not exceed 90 days in a calendar year.
